<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Order Confirmed | Trip’s Sweet Treats</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #111111;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }

    .header {
      background: #000000;
      padding: 40px 28px 26px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      color: #f8d24a;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: #f8d24a;
    }

    .subtext {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      color: #d2d2d2;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px 28px 34px;
    }

    p {
      color: #d8d8d8;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
    }

    .product-box,
    .info-box {
      background: #121212;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .product-title {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: #f8d24a;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .product-copy {
      margin: 0;
      color: #e8e8e8;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .list-title {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: #f8d24a;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .steps {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: #e8e8e8;
    }

    .steps li {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cta-row {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f8d24a;
      color: #111111;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .fine-print {
      margin-top: 22px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #9d9d9d;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .wrap {
        margin: 30px auto;
        padding: 14px;
      }

      .header {
        padding: 32px 20px 22px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 24px 20px 28px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="eyebrow">Order Confirmed</div>
        <h1>You Got One.</h1>
        <p class="subtext">
          Your Lemon Blueberry Pound Cake order is confirmed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Nice move. Your order is in, and your cake is officially claimed from this drop.
        </p>

        <div class="product-box">
          <h2 class="product-title">Old Fashioned Lemon Blueberry Pound Cake</h2>
          <p class="product-copy">
            Rich, buttery pound cake with bright lemon flavor, blueberries baked all the way through, and a light glaze for the perfect sweet-tart finish.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <h3 class="list-title">What happens next:</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li>You’ll receive your order confirmation details by email.</li>
            <li>Your cake will be prepared as part of this limited batch.</li>
            <li>You’ll get pickup or delivery details once your order is ready.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <p>
          This was a limited drop, so once the remaining cakes are gone, that’s it.
        </p>

        <p>
          Keep an eye on your email for any updates and future drop announcements.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a href="https://tripssweettreats.com" class="btn">Back to Site</a>
        </div>

        <p class="fine-print">
          Thanks for ordering from Trip’s Sweet Treats. Limited drops. Real homemade cake. No sad mass-produced nonsense.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
